{"tid":1104453,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"嘉偉黑店","createTime":"2019-04-13T07:02:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-13T07:02:57.000Z","uid":248172,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d30cb36044fd5e3839f60dfd5010301d85e55735","tid":1104453,"uid":248172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T07:02:57.000Z","msg":"上個月同女扑完野覺得唔對路，急急腳想搵間野check check<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上網見呢間嘉偉男士健康中心幾抵又聽過下名，一試就中伏。<br />\n<br />\n本身話醫生診費$680，去到就講$680-1000不等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n果陣唔識野又無其他揀，頂硬上。<br />\n<br />\n過程5分鐘傾完，醫生講的野同網上的資料無分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />然後係咁說我買佢地的全方位化驗package，又大我好多病唔醫生睇唔出要靠化驗，就係咁無多$2500<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n完左之後開藥先離譜，打支針$600，抗生素$600，埋單差唔多$4500<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />小弟淆底又唔識野中招，係到分享等大家小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}